com.yworks.yfiles.graph.styles

Class TableNodeStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.graph.styles.TableNodeStyle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INodeStyle, ICloneable, Cloneable

    public class TableNodeStyle
extends Object
implements INodeStyle, Cloneable
    A INodeStyle for tables.

    This implementations stores the table instance and therefore, its instances cannot be shared among different table instances.
